title: Q - Quercus robur
description: At first, I couldn't think of anything for letter Q. Then I remembered the oak trees are in the genus Quercus! Perfect, I thought. The Quercus robur trees in the woods behind my house are just coming back to life and their fresh leaves are beautiful. I just had to go out at the right moment, when the sun was shining after the rain. And now I will need to take a little break from this series. I'm going to be out for the weekend, and I don't have anything yet for the next letters. I should be back sometime next week with letter R. Thanks to everyone who has been following this project, and I wish you all a wonderful weekend!
label: Original
